00:43:22,560 --> 00:43:24,740
 Molimo te,

612
00:43:24,740 --> 00:43:25,440
 gospodine,

613
00:43:25,440 --> 00:43:28,880
 neka po ovoj molitvi

614
00:43:28,880 --> 00:43:32,340
 raste,

615
00:43:32,340 --> 00:43:34,900
 raste naše zajedništvo s tobom.

616
00:43:34,900 --> 00:43:37,040
 Molimo te,

617
00:43:37,040 --> 00:43:37,780
 gospodine,

618
00:43:37,780 --> 00:43:40,500
 neka milost duha svetoga

619
00:43:40,500 --> 00:43:41,620
 nas sve blagoslovi.

620
00:43:43,020 --> 00:43:43,800
 gospodine,

621
00:43:43,800 --> 00:43:47,820
 ti si tako ljubio svijet,

622
00:43:47,820 --> 00:43:49,960
 sve nas.

623
00:43:49,960 --> 00:43:53,860
 Molimo te,

624
00:43:53,860 --> 00:43:54,620
 gospodine,

625
00:43:55,480 --> 00:43:59,300
 da nas blagosloviš.

626
00:43:59,300 --> 00:44:02,880
 Posebno, Isuse,

627
00:44:02,880 --> 00:44:04,300
 te molim za bolesne,

628
00:44:04,300 --> 00:44:07,360
 za mlade,

629
00:44:07,360 --> 00:44:09,760
 izgubljene,

630
00:44:09,760 --> 00:44:13,160
 za cijeli naš narod,

631
00:44:13,160 --> 00:44:14,140
 našu domovinu,

632
00:44:14,140 --> 00:44:16,540
 za naš radio,

633
00:44:16,540 --> 00:44:18,120
 sve slušatelje.

634
00:44:18,120 --> 00:44:21,180
 Ti si tako divan,

635
00:44:21,180 --> 00:44:21,780
 gospodine.

636
00:44:21,780 --> 00:44:24,640
 Blagoslovi nas.

637
00:44:25,480 --> 00:44:27,960
 Molim te,

638
00:44:27,960 --> 00:44:28,400
 Isuse,

639
00:44:28,400 --> 00:44:33,100
 izliju naša srca povjerenje.

640
00:44:33,100 --> 00:44:36,260
 Povjerenje gdje god krenemo,

641
00:44:36,260 --> 00:44:39,480
 da s tobom idemo.

642
00:44:39,480 --> 00:44:43,280
 Hvala ti, Isuse.

643
00:44:43,280 --> 00:44:47,520
 Sada ćemo zazvati duha svetoga.

644
00:44:47,520 --> 00:44:51,260
 Otvori svoje srce,

645
00:44:51,260 --> 00:44:52,200
 svoje misli.

646
00:44:52,200 --> 00:44:55,460
 Budi poput prazne posude,

647
00:44:55,480 --> 00:44:56,540
 koja samo upija.

648
00:44:56,540 --> 00:44:59,540
 Nemoj ništa raditi,

649
00:44:59,540 --> 00:45:01,280
 nemoj ništa misliti.

650
00:45:01,280 --> 00:45:04,940
 Samo to se dopusti voljati sada.

651
00:45:09,400 --> 00:45:13,140
 dođi duše sveti,

652
00:45:13,140 --> 00:45:14,240
 duše boga živoga,

653
00:45:14,240 --> 00:45:15,180
 duše ljubavi,

654
00:45:15,180 --> 00:45:17,620
 podigni nas,

655
00:45:17,620 --> 00:45:18,800
 Isuse, iz pepela.

656
00:45:18,800 --> 00:45:21,840
 Ražari u nama,

657
00:45:21,840 --> 00:45:22,540
 gospodine,

658
00:45:22,540 --> 00:45:23,140
 vjeru,

659
00:45:23,140 --> 00:45:25,380
 nadu, ljubav,

660
00:45:25,380 --> 00:45:26,420
 ufanju u tebe.

661
00:45:26,420 --> 00:45:29,500
 Dođi duše sveti,

662
00:45:29,500 --> 00:45:31,120
 duše ljubavi,

663
00:45:31,120 --> 00:45:32,800
 radosti.

664
00:45:34,600 --> 00:45:35,440
 Hvala ti, Isuse.

665
00:45:35,440 --> 00:45:38,200
 Blagoslovi ih i čuvaj.

666
00:45:38,200 --> 00:45:40,240
 To te molimo,

667
00:45:40,240 --> 00:45:41,580
 po Kristu,

668
00:45:41,580 --> 00:45:42,740
 gospodinu našemu.

669
00:45:43,240 --> 00:45:44,740
 Amen.

